name: Tunnel (Cyaygel)
description:
Tunnel is an endless mini game which you try to avoid obstacles and survive in the tunnel. 

Every time you jump you get 1 point, every time you destroy an obstacle you get 2 points. 

Try to beat your highscore!

Recomended to play on mobile.

Have Fun!!

Çınar.

Note: Audio spectrum doesn't work on WebGL
